dct_title_s: Spain 1:1,500. Seville city plan. A.M.S. M981
dct_description_sm: Map shows military and coast guard headquarters. Some streets and buildings are named. Oriented with north toward the upper right. " Copied from I.S.I.S. report 1:7,900; Seville, CB 8111 no. 7, 1941. Grid and projection approximate." "Army Map Service, U. S. Army, Washington, D. C. 114807. 1943. 3-43." Military grid. AMS 1 Alternate title: Seville city plan. Copied from I.S.I.S. report 1;7,900, Seville CB 1811 no. 7, 1941. In upper left margin: "Spain 1:7,500". Projection approximate.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1943.
